info.title: IAM
info.description: The documentation for the StackOne Unified API - IAM

value.description: The type of the permission, e.g. read, read_write, delete, etc.
The type of the resource, e.g. user, group, permission, etc.

resources.description: The resources that the permission applies to.

permissions.description: The set of permissions associated with the policy.

policies.description: The set of policies associated with the role.

parent_id.description: The parent group id for when a group belongs to another group.

remote_parent_id.description: Provider's unique identifier of the parent group id for when a group belongs to another group.

value.description: The status of the user, e.g. whether the user is enabled, has been disabled (eg. by an admin), or is pending (ie: awaiting approval by the user or an admin).
The unified value for the type of multi-factor authentication. If the provider does not send back a type but does specify that MFA is set-up for this user, the value will be set to 'unknown'.'
The file format of the file, expressed as a file extension

url.description: URL where the file content is located

unified_url.description: Unified download URL for retrieving file content.

file_format.description: The file format of the file

path.description: The path where the file is stored

contents.description: The content of the file. Deprecated, use `url` and `file_format` one level up instead

created_at.description: The creation date of the file

updated_at.description: The update date of the file

remote_url.description: URL where the file content is located

file_format.description: The file format of the file

unified_custom_fields.description: Custom Unified Fields configured in your StackOne project

primary_email_address.description: Primary email address of the user. This is generally a work email address.

name.description: User's name which (can be a full name or display name)

is_bot_user.description: Indicates if the user is a bot or service user

roles.description: List of roles the user is assigned to

groups.description: List of groups the user is assigned to

last_active_at.description: The date this user was last active

last_login_at.description: The date this user last logged in

created_at.description: The date the user was created

updated_at.description: The date the user was created

multi_factor_enabled.description: The list of Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) types enabled for the user.

avatar.description: The user's avatar data. This generally contains a URL within this property's 'contents' array.
